  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How can I convert a Facebook video to mp3 format?",
  "response": "Converting a Facebook video to MP3 format can be done through a few methods. Here are some common approaches:\n\n### 1. **Using Online Converters:**\nThere are various online tools available that can convert videos from platforms like Facebook to MP3. Here\u2019s how to use them:\n\n1. **Find the Video:** Go to Facebook and locate the video you want to convert. Right-click on the video and select \u201cCopy video URL\u201d or copy the URL from the address bar.\n   \n2. **Choose an Online Converter:** Search for online services like:\n   - YTMP3\n   - Online Video Converter\n   - FLVTO\n\n3. **Paste the URL:** Open the chosen online converter in your browser, paste the copied URL into the provided field.\n\n4. **Select MP3 as the Output Format:** If necessary, select MP3 as the output format.\n\n5. **Download the Converted File:** Click on the convert button, and once the process completes, download the MP3 file to your device.\n\n### 2. **Using Software:**\nYou can use software like VLC Media Player or dedicated converters (e.g., Any Video Converter) to convert videos:\n\n1. **VLC Media Player:**\n   - Open VLC and navigate to **Media > Convert / Save**.\n   - Paste the URL in the **Network** tab and click **Convert / Save**.\n   - Choose the output profile for audio (such as \"Audio - MP3\").\n   - Set the destination file and click **Start**.\n\n2. **Dedicated Software:**\n   - Download and install software like Any Video Converter.\n   - Choose Facebook as the source and paste the video link.\n   - Select MP3 as the output format and start the conversion.\n\n### 3. **Using Chrome Extensions:**\nYou can use browser extensions that allow downloading and converting videos directly from your browser. Look for extensions that specifically mention video to audio conversion.\n\n### Important Notes:\n- **Respect Copyright:** Always ensure you have permission to download and convert audio or video content, especially if it's copyrighted material.\n- **Ad Blockers:** Some online converters may display ads, so using an ad blocker might enhance your experience.\n- **Privacy:** Be cautious when using online services with personal or sensitive data.\n\nBy following these steps, you should be able to successfully convert a Facebook video to MP3 format.",
